<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Campus Life</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Academic/campuslife.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&family=Droid+Serif:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Life at KASH Campus</h1>
            <p>An environment for holistic development and academic excellence.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <section class="intro-section">
                <p>
                    At our school, we strive to provide our students with an exceptional educational experience that goes beyond traditional learning. Here are some of the features that set us apart:
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="campus-life-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-university"></i></div>
                    <h4>Discipline & Focus</h4>
                    <p>We maintain a school-like discipline that fosters a sense of order and respect, preparing students for success in all aspects of life.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i></div>
                    <h4>Quality Teaching</h4>
                    <p>Our teaching is of such high quality that private coaching is unnecessary. Students receive comprehensive orientation for entrance exams from day one.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i></div>
                    <h4>Personal Attention</h4>
                    <p>We believe in personal attention, and our highly qualified teachers provide individualized support to each student to help them reach their full potential.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-language"></i></div>
                    <h4>Bridge Courses</h4>
                    <p>We offer bridge courses from Oriya to English and communicative English courses, ensuring no student is left behind.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-users-cog"></i></div>
                    <h4>Personality Development</h4>
                    <p>We offer personality development classes and a "home away from home" hostel facility to ensure students are well-rounded and happy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-spa"></i></div>
                    <h4>Holistic Wellness</h4>
                    <p>Education is not just about academics, which is why we offer yoga, spiritualism, cultural programs, and quiz programs as part of our routine.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>